				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5083930#post-3693909</guid>
				<title>Round 2</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5083930/scp-3417#post-3693909</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2018 01:49:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>NatVoltaic</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2800867</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So a month or so ago I posted SCP-3417, and after seeing it get mixed reviews I decided to rewrite this. The whole article's been overhauled from it's original version, and aside from central ideas of the anomaly and Ortothan extraterrestrial stuff everything's different now.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" >mlister</a></span>, <span class="error-inline"><em>Varaxous</em> does not match any existing user name</span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009732&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695003" alt="Moklin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009732)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" >Moklin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" >Mortos</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" >Tufto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span> for reading and giving crit, and thanks to everyone that left feedback in the original discussion thread.</p> <p>Fun fact that isn't directly stated in the article because I couldn't think of a good place to put it: Those transmissions in the image traveled 28 kilolight-years (28,000 light-years) before reaching Earth and getting detected. This is the earliest transmission from the anomaly that was detected, which means that SCP-3417 has been preaching for at least 28,000 years, and has been alive for longer.</p> <p><a href="http://kaktuskontainer.wikidot.com/sigma:9volt-scp-3417-original">Original Version of SCP-3417</a></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Original&nbsp;Author&nbsp;Post</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Original&nbsp;Author&nbsp;Post</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p><strong>Put on your Sunday clothes, there's lots of world out there!</strong></p> <p>The universe is a busy place.</p> <p>This is the first of more planned articles that involve the large presence of aliens in Ortothan groups, the mythos, and the Church of the Second Hytoth itself (Note that not all Ortothans are a part of the CotSH, that's just the largest Ortothan group on Earth, which is mainly human. There's a lot more groups and lone Ortothans out there.). This will also the first of more planned articles featuring the Extrasolar Activities Department, which should a lot of fun to write.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" >mlister</a></span>, <span class="error-inline"><em>Varaxous</em> does not match any existing user name</span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564695004" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span> for crit!</p> <p>Fun fact that isn't directly stated in the article because I couldn't think of a good place to put it: Those transmissions in the image traveled 28 kilolight-years (28,000 light-years) before reaching Earth and getting detected. This is the earliest transmission from the anomaly that was detected, which means that SCP-3417 has been preaching for at least 28,000 years, and has been alive for longer.</p> <p>Image sources:</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://images.nasa.gov/#/details-8000104.html">https://images.nasa.gov/#/details-8000104.html</a> (<a href="https://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/guidelines/index.html">NASA image use guidelines</a>)</li> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Carbon_Planet.JPG">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Carbon_Planet.JPG</a></li> </ul> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <p>Image sources:</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://images.nasa.gov/#/details-8000104.html">https://images.nasa.gov/#/details-8000104.html</a> (<a href="https://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/guidelines/index.html">NASA image use guidelines</a>)</li> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Two_Brown_Dwarfs_in_Our_Backyard.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Two_Brown_Dwarfs_in_Our_Backyard.jpg</a></li> </ul> 
				 	]]>
